<GUIClass name="CMUI_YASelectCriteriaCntl" id="6ca0c842-f449-47e5-98ac-b4b60a526493">
    <superclass name="CMUI_BaseControl"/>
    <transient/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <access>protected</access>
    <text>This control contains Jade controls fro selecting criteria for Yard Allocations.

The following is the layout of the Jade controls:
+--------------------------------------------------------+
| Criteria Attribute XXX&lt;Combobox of criteria types&gt;XXX  |
|                                                        |
| +-------------------+            +-------------------+ |
| |                   |  btnAdd    |                   | |
| |     list of       | btnAddAll  |     list of       | |
| |    available      | btnRemove  |     selected      | |
| |      codes        | btnRemAll  |      codes        | |
| |                   |            |                   | |
| +-------------------+            +-------------------+ |
|                              X&lt;BtnAdd&gt;X  X&lt;BtnDelete&gt;X |
| +----------------------------------------------------+ |
| | Voyage: V123, V124                                 | |
| | ISO-Type: 2040, 2038                               | |
| | IMEX: Export            &lt;Table&gt;                    | |
| |                                                    | |
| |                                                    | |
| +----------------------------------------------------+ |
+--------------------------------------------------------+</text>
